headline: City of Homestead, Florida, Launches Integrated Online Permitting, Licensing, and Code Enforcement Cloud Suite from Tyler Technologies
summary: PLANO, Texas, November 25, 2025--Tyler Technologies announced that the city of Homestead, Florida, has launched Tyler’s Enterprise Permitting & Licensing cloud platform.

headline: Do Wall Street Analysts Like Tyler Technologies Stock?
summary: Tyler Technologies has severely underperformed the broader market over the past year, yet analysts remain moderately optimistic about the stock’s prospects.
